<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/footer.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/nav-bar') %>

    <section class="page-section">
        <h1 class="section-title">AI Solutions Blog</h1>
        <p class="section-subtitle">Insights, trends, and innovations in artificial intelligence</p>

        <!-- Featured Article -->
        <div class="featured-article">
            <div class="featured-image">
                <img src="/images/blog/ai-future.jpg" alt="The Future of AI">
                <span class="featured-tag">Featured</span>
            </div>
            <div class="featured-content">
                <div class="article-meta">
                    <span class="article-date"><i class="far fa-calendar"></i> March 15, 2024</span>
                    <span class="article-category"><i class="fas fa-tag"></i> AI Trends</span>
                </div>
                <h2>The Future of AI: Transforming Industries in 2024 and Beyond</h2>
                <p>Explore how artificial intelligence is reshaping various sectors and what to expect in the coming years...</p>
                <a href="#" class="read-more">Read Article <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Blog Grid -->
        <div class="blog-grid">
            <article class="blog-card">
                <div class="blog-image">
                    <img src="/images/blog/machine-learning.jpg" alt="Machine Learning">
                </div>
                <div class="blog-content">
                    <div class="article-meta">
                        <span class="article-date"><i class="far fa-calendar"></i> March 10, 2024</span>
                        <span class="article-category"><i class="fas fa-tag"></i> Machine Learning</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Understanding Deep Learning: A Comprehensive Guide</h3>
                    <p>Dive deep into the fundamentals of deep learning and its practical applications in modern businesses...</p>
                    <a href="#" class="read-more">Continue Reading <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="blog-card">
                <div class="blog-image">
                    <img src="/images/blog/chatbots.jpg" alt="AI Chatbots">
                </div>
                <div class="blog-content">
                    <div class="article-meta">
                        <span class="article-date"><i class="far fa-calendar"></i> March 8, 2024</span>
                        <span class="article-category"><i class="fas fa-tag"></i> AI Solutions</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3>How AI Chatbots Are Revolutionizing Customer Service</h3>
                    <p>Discover how AI-powered chatbots are transforming customer service and improving user experience...</p>
                    <a href="#" class="read-more">Continue Reading <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="blog-card">
                <div class="blog-image">
                    <img src="/images/blog/data-analytics.jpg" alt="Data Analytics">
                </div>
                <div class="blog-content">
                    <div class="article-meta">
                        <span class="article-date"><i class="far fa-calendar"></i> March 5, 2024</span>
                        <span class="article-category"><i class="fas fa-tag"></i> Data Analytics</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Predictive Analytics: The Key to Business Intelligence</h3>
                    <p>Learn how predictive analytics is helping businesses make better decisions and forecast future trends...</p>
                    <a href="#" class="read-more">Continue Reading <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="blog-card">
                <div class="blog-image">
                    <img src="/images/blog/ai-security.jpg" alt="AI Security">
                </div>
                <div class="blog-content">
                    <div class="article-meta">
                        <span class="article-date"><i class="far fa-calendar"></i> March 1, 2024</span>
                        <span class="article-category"><i class="fas fa-tag"></i> Security</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3>AI in Cybersecurity: Protecting Digital Assets</h3>
                    <p>Explore how artificial intelligence is strengthening cybersecurity measures and preventing threats...</p>
                    <a href="#" class="read-more">Continue Reading <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
                </div>
            </article>
        </div>

        <!-- Pagination -->
        <div class="pagination">
            <a href="#" class="page-link active">1</a>
            <a href="#" class="page-link">2</a>
            <a href="#" class="page-link">3</a>
            <span class="page-dots">...</span>
            <a href="#" class="page-link">10</a>
            <a href="#" class="page-link next">Next <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html> 